{
  "video_id": "DGvPfD1Dd1U",
  "title": "Need a new idea? Start at the edge of what is known | Vittorio Loreto",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 14349.0,
      "end_time": 17216.0,
      "text": "We have all probably wondered"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17240.0,
      "end_time": 21415.0,
      "text": "how great minds achieved what they achieved, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21440.0,
      "end_time": 24960.0,
      "text": "And the more astonishing their achievements are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24120.0,
      "end_time": 26656.0,
      "text": "the more we call them geniuses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26680.0,
      "end_time": 28216.0,
      "text": "perhaps aliens"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28239.0,
      "end_time": 30336.0,
      "text": "coming from a different planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30360.0,
      "end_time": 33160.0,
      "text": "definitely not someone like us."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33400.0,
      "end_time": 34816.0,
      "text": "But is that true?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34840.0,
      "end_time": 36640.0,
      "text": "So let me start with an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37440.0,
      "end_time": 41256.0,
      "text": "You all know the story of Newton&#39;s apple, right? OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41280.0,
      "end_time": 44216.0,
      "text": "Is that true? Probably not."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44240.0,
      "end_time": 49456.0,
      "text": "Still, it&#39;s difficult to think that no apple at all was there."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49480.0,
      "end_time": 53960.0,
      "text": "I mean some stepping stone, some specific conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53120.0,
      "end_time": 57135.0,
      "text": "that made universal gravitation not impossible to conceive."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57160.0,
      "end_time": 59535.0,
      "text": "And definitely this was not impossible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59560.0,
      "end_time": 61136.0,
      "text": "at least for Newton."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61160.0,
      "end_time": 62416.0,
      "text": "It was possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62440.0,
      "end_time": 65495.0,
      "text": "and for some reason, it was also there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65519.00000000001,
      "end_time": 69295.0,
      "text": "available at some point, easy to pick as an apple."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69320.0,
      "end_time": 70936.0,
      "text": "Here is the apple."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70960.0,
      "end_time": 73175.0,
      "text": "And what about Einstein?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73200.0,
      "end_time": 78496.0,
      "text": "Was relativity theory another big leap in the history of ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78520.0,
      "end_time": 81176.0,
      "text": "no one else could even conceive?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81200.0,
      "end_time": 85656.0,
      "text": "Or rather, was it again something adjacent and possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85680.0,
      "end_time": 87776.0,
      "text": "to Einstein of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87800.0,
      "end_time": 92150.0,
      "text": "and he got there by small steps and his very peculiar scientific path?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 92400.0,
      "end_time": 94496.0,
      "text": "Of course we cannot conceive this path,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94520.0,
      "end_time": 97000.0,
      "text": "but this doesn&#39;t mean that the path was not there."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 98760.0,
      "end_time": 103616.0,
      "text": "So all of this seems very evocative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 103640.0,
      "end_time": 105176.0,
      "text": "but I would say hardly concrete"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 105200.0,
      "end_time": 108776.0,
      "text": "if we really want to grasp the origin of great ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108800.0,
      "end_time": 112816.0,
      "text": "and more generally the way in which the new enters our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112840.0,
      "end_time": 114816.0,
      "text": "As a physicist, as a scientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114840.0,
      "end_time": 117160.0,
      "text": "I have learned that posing the right questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117400.0,
      "end_time": 119560.0,
      "text": "is half of the solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119800.0,
      "end_time": 123816.0,
      "text": "But I think now we start having a great conceptual framework"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123840.0,
      "end_time": 127160.0,
      "text": "to conceive and address the right questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127400.0,
      "end_time": 130496.0,
      "text": "So let me drive you to the edge of what is known,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 130520.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132616.0,
      "text": "or at least, what I know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 132640.0,
      "end_time": 134696.0,
      "text": "and let me show you that what is known"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134720.0,
      "end_time": 139296.0,
      "text": "could be a powerful and fascinating starting point"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 139320.0,
      "end_time": 144416.0,
      "text": "to grasp the deep meaning of words like novelty, innovation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 144440.0,
      "end_time": 146000.0,
      "text": "creativity perhaps."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146880.0,
      "end_time": 150216.0,
      "text": "So we are discussing the \"new,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150240.0,
      "end_time": 152896.0,
      "text": "and of course, the science behind it."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152920.0,
      "end_time": 155896.0,
      "text": "The new can enter our lives in many different ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155920.0,
      "end_time": 157616.0,
      "text": "can be very personal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 157640.0,
      "end_time": 159576.0,
      "text": "like I meet a new person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159600.0,
      "end_time": 162896.0,
      "text": "I read a new book, or I listen to a new song."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162920.0,
      "end_time": 164176.0,
      "text": "Or it could be global,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164200.0,
      "end_time": 166256.0,
      "text": "I mean, something we call innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 166280.0,
      "end_time": 168456.0,
      "text": "It could be a new theory, a new technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 168480.0,
      "end_time": 171550.0,
      "text": "but it could also be a new book if you&#39;re the writer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 171800.0,
      "end_time": 173416.0,
      "text": "or it could be a new song if you&#39;re the composer."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 173440.0,
      "end_time": 177736.0,
      "text": "In all of these global cases, the new is for everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 177760.0,
      "end_time": 181576.0,
      "text": "but experiencing the new can be also frightening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 181600.0,
      "end_time": 185335.0,
      "text": "so the new can also frighten us."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 185360.0,
      "end_time": 189536.0,
      "text": "But still, experiencing the new means exploring a very peculiar space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 189560.0,
      "end_time": 191656.0,
      "text": "the space of what could be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 191680.0,
      "end_time": 194856.0,
      "text": "the space of the possible, the space of possibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 194880.0,
      "end_time": 198335.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a very weird space, so I&#39;ll try to get you through this space."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 198360.0,
      "end_time": 200376.0,
      "text": "So it could be a physical space."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 200400.0,
      "end_time": 202160.0,
      "text": "So in this case, for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 202400.0,
      "end_time": 206960.0,
      "text": "novelty could be climbing Machu Picchu for the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 206120.0,
      "end_time": 208400.0,
      "text": "as I did in 2016."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 208960.0,
      "end_time": 210776.0,
      "text": "It could be a conceptual space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 210800.0,
      "end_time": 215216.0,
      "text": "so acquiring new information, making sense of it, in a word, learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 215240.0,
      "end_time": 217176.0,
      "text": "It could be a biological space."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 217200.0,
      "end_time": 221296.0,
      "text": "I mean, think about the never-ending fight of viruses and bacteria"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 221320.0,
      "end_time": 223256.0,
      "text": "with our immune system."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 223280.0,
      "end_time": 225160.0,
      "text": "And now comes the bad news."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 225400.0,
      "end_time": 228335.0,
      "text": "We are very, very bad at grasping this space."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 228360.0,
      "end_time": 230376.0,
      "text": "Think of it. Let&#39;s make an experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 230400.0,
      "end_time": 237280.0,
      "text": "Try to think about all the possible things you could do in the next, say, 24 hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 238320.0,
      "end_time": 240976.0,
      "text": "Here the key word is \"all.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 241000.0,
      "end_time": 245800.0,
      "text": "Of course you can conceive a few options, like having a drink, writing a letter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 246840.0,
      "end_time": 250160.0,
      "text": "also sleeping during this boring talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 250400.0,
      "end_time": 251736.0,
      "text": "if you can."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 251760.0,
      "end_time": 253416.0,
      "text": "But not all of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 253440.0,
      "end_time": 257375.0,
      "text": "So think about an alien invasion, now, here, in Milan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 257399.0,
      "end_time": 260519.0,
      "text": "or me -- I stopped thinking for 15 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 261440.0,
      "end_time": 264576.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s very difficult to conceive this space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 264600.0,
      "end_time": 266776.0,
      "text": "but actually we have an excuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 266800.0,
      "end_time": 270296.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s not so easy to conceive this space"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 270320.0,
      "end_time": 273815.0,
      "text": "because we are trying to conceive the occurrence of something brand new,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 273839.0,
      "end_time": 275816.0,
      "text": "so something that never occurred before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 275840.0,
      "end_time": 277320.0,
      "text": "so we don&#39;t have clues."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 278400.0,
      "end_time": 280936.0,
      "text": "A typical solution could be"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 280960.0,
      "end_time": 284176.0,
      "text": "looking at the future with the eyes of the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 284200.0,
      "end_time": 287496.0,
      "text": "so relying on all the time series of past events"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 287520.0,
      "end_time": 291150.0,
      "text": "and hoping that this is enough to predict the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 291400.0,
      "end_time": 293216.0,
      "text": "But we know this is not working."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 293240.0,
      "end_time": 298456.0,
      "text": "For instance, this was the first attempt for weather forecasts, and it failed."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 298480.0,
      "end_time": 300896.0,
      "text": "And it failed because of the great complexity"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 300920.0,
      "end_time": 302856.0,
      "text": "of the underlying phenomenon."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 302880.0,
      "end_time": 308496.0,
      "text": "So now we know that predictions had to be based on modeling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 308520.0,
      "end_time": 312150.0,
      "text": "which means creating a synthetic model of the system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 312400.0,
      "end_time": 316176.0,
      "text": "simulating this model and then projecting the system"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 316200.0,
      "end_time": 318736.0,
      "text": "into the future through this model."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 318760.0,
      "end_time": 321695.0,
      "text": "And now we can do this in a lot of cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 321720.0,
      "end_time": 323600.0,
      "text": "with the help of a lot of data."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 325000.0,
      "end_time": 327896.0,
      "text": "Looking at the future with the eye of the past"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 327920.0,
      "end_time": 330656.0,
      "text": "could be misleading also for machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 330680.0,
      "end_time": 331896.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 331920.0,
      "end_time": 336720.0,
      "text": "Now picture yourself for a second in the middle of the Australian Outback."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 337440.0,
      "end_time": 340160.0,
      "text": "You stand there under the sun."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 340840.0,
      "end_time": 343560.0,
      "text": "So you see something weird happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 343800.0,
      "end_time": 345816.0,
      "text": "The car suddenly stops"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 345840.0,
      "end_time": 348895.0,
      "text": "very, very far from a kangaroo crossing the street."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 348920.0,
      "end_time": 350376.0,
      "text": "You look closer"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 350400.0,
      "end_time": 352816.0,
      "text": "and you realize that the car has no driver."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 352840.0,
      "end_time": 356856.0,
      "text": "It is not restarting, even after the kangaroo is not there anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 356880.0,
      "end_time": 358776.0,
      "text": "So for some reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 358800.0,
      "end_time": 361336.0,
      "text": "the algorithms driving the car cannot make sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 361360.0,
      "end_time": 365400.0,
      "text": "of this strange beast jumping here and there on the street."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 365640.0,
      "end_time": 366840.0,
      "text": "So it just stops."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 367720.0,
      "end_time": 369856.0,
      "text": "Now, I should tell you, this is a true story."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 369880.0,
      "end_time": 372576.0,
      "text": "It happened a few months ago to Volvo&#39;s self-driving cars"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 372600.0,
      "end_time": 374536.0,
      "text": "in the middle of the Australian Outback."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 374560.0,
      "end_time": 376256.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 376280.0,
      "end_time": 378256.0,
      "text": "It is a general problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 378280.0,
      "end_time": 381256.0,
      "text": "and I guess this will affect more and more in the near future"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 381280.0,
      "end_time": 383840.0,
      "text": "artificial intelligence and machine learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 384440.0,
      "end_time": 388416.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also a very old problem, I would say 17th century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 388440.0,
      "end_time": 393576.0,
      "text": "but I guess now we have new tools and new clues to start solving it."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 393600.0,
      "end_time": 395776.0,
      "text": "So let me take a step back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 395800.0,
      "end_time": 398536.0,
      "text": "five years back."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 398560.0,
      "end_time": 401536.0,
      "text": "Italy. Rome. Winter."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 401560.0,
      "end_time": 405136.0,
      "text": "So the winter of 2012 was very special in Rome."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 405160.0,
      "end_time": 408720.0,
      "text": "Rome witnessed one of the greatest snowfalls of its history."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 409520.0,
      "end_time": 413216.0,
      "text": "That winter was special also for me and my colleagues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 413240.0,
      "end_time": 416736.0,
      "text": "because we had an insight about the possible mathematical scheme --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 416760.0,
      "end_time": 419736.0,
      "text": "again, possible, possible mathematical scheme,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 419760.0,
      "end_time": 421599.0,
      "text": "to conceive the occurrence of the new."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 422520.0,
      "end_time": 424936.0,
      "text": "I remember that day because it was snowing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 424960.0,
      "end_time": 428736.0,
      "text": "so due to the snowfall, we were blocked, stuck in my department,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 428760.0,
      "end_time": 430176.0,
      "text": "and we couldn&#39;t go home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 430200.0,
      "end_time": 433256.0,
      "text": "so we got another coffee, we relaxed"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 433280.0,
      "end_time": 435560.0,
      "text": "and we kept discussing."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 435800.0,
      "end_time": 438776.0,
      "text": "But at some point -- maybe not that date, precisely --"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 438800.0,
      "end_time": 441696.0,
      "text": "at some point we made the connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 441720.0,
      "end_time": 444696.0,
      "text": "between the problem of the new"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 444720.0,
      "end_time": 447136.0,
      "text": "and a beautiful concept proposed years before"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 447160.0,
      "end_time": 448936.0,
      "text": "by Stuart Kauffman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 448960.0,
      "end_time": 451000.0,
      "text": "the adjacent possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 451720.0,
      "end_time": 454776.0,
      "text": "So the adjacent possible consists of all those things."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 454800.0,
      "end_time": 458536.0,
      "text": "It could be ideas, it could be molecules, it could be technological products"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 458560.0,
      "end_time": 461496.0,
      "text": "that are one step away"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 461520.0,
      "end_time": 463256.0,
      "text": "from what actually exists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 463280.0,
      "end_time": 466816.0,
      "text": "and you can achieve them through incremental modifications"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 466840.0,
      "end_time": 469400.0,
      "text": "and recombinations of the existing material."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 470520.0,
      "end_time": 474416.0,
      "text": "So for instance, if I speak about the space of my friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 474440.0,
      "end_time": 478416.0,
      "text": "my adjacent possible would be the set of all friends of my friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 478440.0,
      "end_time": 479840.0,
      "text": "not already my friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 480240.0,
      "end_time": 481976.0,
      "text": "I hope that&#39;s clear."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 482000.0,
      "end_time": 483816.0,
      "text": "But now if I meet a new person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 483840.0,
      "end_time": 485536.0,
      "text": "say Briar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 485560.0,
      "end_time": 489616.0,
      "text": "all her friends would immediately enter my adjacent possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 489640.0,
      "end_time": 491159.0,
      "text": "pushing its boundaries further."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 492160.0,
      "end_time": 495376.0,
      "text": "So if you really want to look from the mathematical point of view --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 495400.0,
      "end_time": 496799.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure you want --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 498200.0,
      "end_time": 500176.0,
      "text": "you can actually look at this picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 500200.0,
      "end_time": 502960.0,
      "text": "So suppose now this is your universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 502120.0,
      "end_time": 503376.0,
      "text": "I know I&#39;m asking a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 503400.0,
      "end_time": 506390.0,
      "text": "I mean, this is your universe. Now you are the red spot."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 507320.0,
      "end_time": 509936.0,
      "text": "And the green spot is the adjacent possible for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 509960.0,
      "end_time": 512550.0,
      "text": "so something you&#39;ve never touched before."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 512799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 513415.99999999994,
      "text": "So you do your normal life."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 513440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515960.00000000006,
      "text": "You move. You move in the space."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 515120.0,
      "end_time": 517775.0,
      "text": "You have a drink. You meet friends. You read a book."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 517799.0,
      "end_time": 520695.0,
      "text": "At some point, you end up on the green spot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 520720.0,
      "end_time": 522896.0,
      "text": "so you meet Briar for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 522919.0,
      "end_time": 524256.0,
      "text": "And what happens?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 524280.0,
      "end_time": 526576.0,
      "text": "So what happens is there is a new part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 526600.0,
      "end_time": 529560.0,
      "text": "a brand new part of the space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 529800.0,
      "end_time": 533336.0,
      "text": "becoming possible for you in this very moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 533360.0,
      "end_time": 537216.0,
      "text": "even without any possibility for you to foresee this"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 537240.0,
      "end_time": 539296.0,
      "text": "before touching that point."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 539320.0,
      "end_time": 542160.0,
      "text": "And behind this there will be a huge set of points"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 542400.0,
      "end_time": 545736.0,
      "text": "that could become possible at some later stages."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 545760.0,
      "end_time": 548576.0,
      "text": "So you see the space of the possible is very peculiar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 548600.0,
      "end_time": 550816.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s not predefined."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 550840.0,
      "end_time": 553136.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not something we can predefine."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 553160.0,
      "end_time": 556536.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something that gets continuously shaped and reshaped"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 556560.0,
      "end_time": 559160.0,
      "text": "by our actions and our choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 560120.0,
      "end_time": 563576.0,
      "text": "So we were so fascinated by these connections we made --"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 563600.0,
      "end_time": 565496.0,
      "text": "scientists are like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 565520.0,
      "end_time": 567816.0,
      "text": "And based on this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 567840.0,
      "end_time": 571560.0,
      "text": "we conceived our mathematical formulation for the adjacent possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 571800.0,
      "end_time": 574536.0,
      "text": "20 years after the original Kauffman proposals."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 574560.0,
      "end_time": 576695.0,
      "text": "In our theory -- this is a key point --"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 576720.0,
      "end_time": 580256.0,
      "text": "I mean, it&#39;s crucially based on a complex interplay"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 580280.0,
      "end_time": 585550.0,
      "text": "between the way in which this space of possibilities expands"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 585800.0,
      "end_time": 586616.0,
      "text": "and gets restructured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 586640.0,
      "end_time": 589136.0,
      "text": "and the way in which we explore it."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 589160.0,
      "end_time": 593160.0,
      "text": "After the epiphany of 2012,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 593400.0,
      "end_time": 594695.0,
      "text": "we got back to work, real work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 594720.0,
      "end_time": 596616.0,
      "text": "because we had to work out this theory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 596640.0,
      "end_time": 599560.0,
      "text": "and we came up with a certain number of predictions"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 599800.0,
      "end_time": 600336.0,
      "text": "to be tested in real life."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 600360.0,
      "end_time": 603256.0,
      "text": "Of course, we need a testable framework"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 603280.0,
      "end_time": 604736.0,
      "text": "to study innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 604760.0,
      "end_time": 608816.0,
      "text": "So let me drive you across a few predictions we made."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 608840.0,
      "end_time": 611736.0,
      "text": "The first one concerns the pace of innovation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 611760.0,
      "end_time": 616656.0,
      "text": "so the rate at which you observe novelties in very different systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 616680.0,
      "end_time": 619175.0,
      "text": "So our theory predicts that the rate of innovation"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 619200.0,
      "end_time": 621136.0,
      "text": "should follow a universal curve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 621160.0,
      "end_time": 622480.0,
      "text": "like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 623240.0,
      "end_time": 626880.0,
      "text": "This is the rate of innovation versus time in very different conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 627720.0,
      "end_time": 630336.0,
      "text": "And somehow, we predict that the rate of innovation"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 630360.0,
      "end_time": 633560.0,
      "text": "should decrease steadily over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 633800.0,
      "end_time": 636176.0,
      "text": "So somehow, innovation is predicted to become more difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 636200.0,
      "end_time": 638120.0,
      "text": "as your progress over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 638960.0,
      "end_time": 642496.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s neat. It&#39;s interesting. It&#39;s beautiful. We were happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 642520.0,
      "end_time": 644696.0,
      "text": "But the question is, is that true?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 644720.0,
      "end_time": 646600.0,
      "text": "Of course we should check with reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 647600.0,
      "end_time": 649976.0,
      "text": "So we went back to reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 650000.0,
      "end_time": 653136.0,
      "text": "and we collected a lot of data, terabytes of data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 653160.0,
      "end_time": 656496.0,
      "text": "tracking innovation in Wikipedia, Twitter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 656520.0,
      "end_time": 658736.0,
      "text": "the way in which we write free software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 658760.0,
      "end_time": 660400.0,
      "text": "even the way we listen to music."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 661160.0,
      "end_time": 664896.0,
      "text": "I cannot tell you, we were so amazed and pleased and thrilled"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 664920.0,
      "end_time": 668415.0,
      "text": "to discover that the same predictions we made in the theory"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 668440.0,
      "end_time": 671160.0,
      "text": "were actually satisfied in real systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 671400.0,
      "end_time": 672575.0,
      "text": "many different real systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 672600.0,
      "end_time": 674960.0,
      "text": "We were so excited."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 674120.0,
      "end_time": 676936.0,
      "text": "Of course, apparently, we were on the right track,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 676960.0,
      "end_time": 679456.0,
      "text": "but of course, we couldn&#39;t stop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 679480.0,
      "end_time": 680976.0,
      "text": "so we didn&#39;t stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 681000.0,
      "end_time": 683960.0,
      "text": "So we kept going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 683120.0,
      "end_time": 685176.0,
      "text": "and at some point we made another discovery"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 685200.0,
      "end_time": 688736.0,
      "text": "that we dubbed \"correlated novelties.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 688760.0,
      "end_time": 690160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 690400.0,
      "end_time": 691935.0,
      "text": "So I guess we all experience this."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 691960.0,
      "end_time": 695520.0,
      "text": "So you listen to \"Suzanne\" by Leonard Cohen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 696440.0,
      "end_time": 700960.0,
      "text": "and this experience triggers your passion for Cohen"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 700120.0,
      "end_time": 703936.0,
      "text": "so that you start frantically listening to his whole production."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 703960.0,
      "end_time": 706256.0,
      "text": "And then you realize that Fabrizio De André here"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 706280.0,
      "end_time": 708256.0,
      "text": "recorded an Italian version of \"Suzanne,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 708280.0,
      "end_time": 710295.0,
      "text": "and so on and so forth."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 710320.0,
      "end_time": 712296.0,
      "text": "So somehow for some reason,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 712320.0,
      "end_time": 716216.0,
      "text": "the very notion of adjacent possible is already encoding the common belief"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 716240.0,
      "end_time": 718800.0,
      "text": "that one thing leads to another"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 719720.0,
      "end_time": 721456.0,
      "text": "in many different systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 721480.0,
      "end_time": 723776.0,
      "text": "But the reason why we were thrilled"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 723800.0,
      "end_time": 726324.0,
      "text": "is because actually we could give, for the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 726348.0,
      "end_time": 728415.0,
      "text": "a scientific substance to this intuition"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 728440.0,
      "end_time": 730960.0,
      "text": "and start making predictions"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 730120.0,
      "end_time": 732536.0,
      "text": "about the way in which we experience the new."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 732560.0,
      "end_time": 734880.0,
      "text": "So novelties are correlated."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 736320.0,
      "end_time": 738376.0,
      "text": "They are not occurring randomly."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 738400.0,
      "end_time": 739856.0,
      "text": "And this is good news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 739880.0,
      "end_time": 744616.0,
      "text": "because it implies that impossible missions"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 744640.0,
      "end_time": 747160.0,
      "text": "might not be so impossible after all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 747400.0,
      "end_time": 750136.0,
      "text": "if we are guided by our intuition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 750160.0,
      "end_time": 753920.0,
      "text": "somehow leading us to trigger a positive chain reaction."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 754840.0,
      "end_time": 758336.0,
      "text": "But there is a third consequence of the existence of the adjacent possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 758360.0,
      "end_time": 761896.0,
      "text": "that we named \"waves of novelties.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 761920.0,
      "end_time": 764616.0,
      "text": "So just to make this simple, so in music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 764640.0,
      "end_time": 766160.0,
      "text": "without waves of novelties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 766400.0,
      "end_time": 772960.0,
      "text": "we would still be listening all the time to Mozart or Beethoven,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 772120.0,
      "end_time": 773616.0,
      "text": "which is great,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 773640.0,
      "end_time": 775295.0,
      "text": "but we don&#39;t do this all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 775320.0,
      "end_time": 780336.0,
      "text": "We also listen to the Pet Shop Boys or Justin Bieber -- well, some of us do."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 780360.0,
      "end_time": 782536.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 782560.0,
      "end_time": 786455.0,
      "text": "So we could see very clearly all of these patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 786480.0,
      "end_time": 790216.0,
      "text": "in the huge amounts of data we collected and analyzed."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 790240.0,
      "end_time": 793896.0,
      "text": "For instance, we discovered that popular hits in music"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 793920.0,
      "end_time": 795815.0,
      "text": "are continuously born, you know that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 795840.0,
      "end_time": 799280.0,
      "text": "and then they disappear, still leaving room for evergreens."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 800120.0,
      "end_time": 803216.0,
      "text": "So somehow waves of novelties ebb and flow"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 803240.0,
      "end_time": 805816.0,
      "text": "while the tides always hold the classics."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 805840.0,
      "end_time": 809800.0,
      "text": "There is this coexistence between evergreens and new hits."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 811920.0,
      "end_time": 814616.0,
      "text": "Not only our theory predicts these waves of novelties."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 814640.0,
      "end_time": 816960.0,
      "text": "This would be trivial."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 816120.0,
      "end_time": 819160.0,
      "text": "But it also explains why they are there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 819400.0,
      "end_time": 821160.0,
      "text": "and they are there for a specific reason,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 821400.0,
      "end_time": 824256.0,
      "text": "because we as humans display different strategies"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 824280.0,
      "end_time": 826136.0,
      "text": "in the space of the possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 826160.0,
      "end_time": 831295.0,
      "text": "So some of us tend to retrace already known paths."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 831320.0,
      "end_time": 833640.0,
      "text": "So we say they exploit."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 834360.0,
      "end_time": 837216.0,
      "text": "Some of us always launch into new adventures."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 837240.0,
      "end_time": 838936.0,
      "text": "We say they explore."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 838960.0,
      "end_time": 842256.0,
      "text": "And what we discovered is all the systems we investigated"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 842280.0,
      "end_time": 845456.0,
      "text": "are right at the edge between these two strategies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 845480.0,
      "end_time": 849160.0,
      "text": "something like 80 percent exploiting, 20 percent exploring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 849400.0,
      "end_time": 851719.0,
      "text": "something like blade runners of innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 852720.0,
      "end_time": 857936.0,
      "text": "So it seems that the wise balance, you could also say a conservative balance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 857960.0,
      "end_time": 862936.0,
      "text": "between past and future, between exploitation and exploration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 862960.0,
      "end_time": 866376.0,
      "text": "is already in place and perhaps needed in our system."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 866400.0,
      "end_time": 870160.0,
      "text": "But again the good news is now we have scientific tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 870400.0,
      "end_time": 871776.0,
      "text": "to investigate this equilibrium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 871800.0,
      "end_time": 875790.0,
      "text": "perhaps pushing it further in the near future."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 877360.0,
      "end_time": 879616.0,
      "text": "So as you can imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 879640.0,
      "end_time": 883800.0,
      "text": "I was really fascinated by all this."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 884920.0,
      "end_time": 888550.0,
      "text": "Our mathematical scheme is already providing cues and hints"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 888800.0,
      "end_time": 890136.0,
      "text": "to investigate the space of possibilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 890160.0,
      "end_time": 894175.0,
      "text": "and the way in which all of us create it and explore it."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 894200.0,
      "end_time": 895536.0,
      "text": "But there is more."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 895560.0,
      "end_time": 898935.0,
      "text": "This, I guess, is a starting point of something that has the potential"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 898960.0,
      "end_time": 903576.0,
      "text": "to become a wonderful journey for a scientific investigation of the new,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 903600.0,
      "end_time": 906880.0,
      "text": "but also I would say a personal investigation of the new."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 909320.0,
      "end_time": 912216.0,
      "text": "And I guess this can have a lot of consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 912240.0,
      "end_time": 914376.0,
      "text": "and a huge impact in key activities"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 914400.0,
      "end_time": 919720.0,
      "text": "like learning, education, research, business."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 920680.0,
      "end_time": 923575.0,
      "text": "So for instance, if you think about artificial intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 923600.0,
      "end_time": 925736.0,
      "text": "I am sure -- I mean, artificial intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 925760.0,
      "end_time": 927576.0,
      "text": "we need to rely in the near future"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 927600.0,
      "end_time": 931416.0,
      "text": "more and more on the structure of the adjacent possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 931440.0,
      "end_time": 933376.0,
      "text": "to restructure it, to change it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 933400.0,
      "end_time": 935720.0,
      "text": "but also to cope with the unknowns of the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 936400.0,
      "end_time": 938256.0,
      "text": "In parallel, we have a lot of tools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 938280.0,
      "end_time": 941776.0,
      "text": "new tools now, to investigate how creativity works"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 941800.0,
      "end_time": 943400.0,
      "text": "and what triggers innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 944800.0,
      "end_time": 947256.0,
      "text": "And the aim of all this is to raise a generation of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 947280.0,
      "end_time": 950896.0,
      "text": "able to come up with new ideas to face the challenges in front of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 950920.0,
      "end_time": 952136.0,
      "text": "We all know."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 952160.0,
      "end_time": 954256.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s a long way to go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 954280.0,
      "end_time": 957336.0,
      "text": "but the questions, and the tools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 957360.0,
      "end_time": 960920.0,
      "text": "are now there, adjacent and possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 961720.0,
      "end_time": 962936.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 962960.0,
      "end_time": 967840.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}